# Purpose....: Template for archivelog restore
# Notes......: Restores archivelogs by sequence number range.
#              Replace <FIRST_SEQUENCE> and <LAST_SEQUENCE> with actual values.
#              For RAC, adjust thread parameter accordingly.
#              Converted from TVD Backup template to OraDBA format.
# Reference..: https://github.com/oehrlis/oradba
